About the game: What is CatNab? CatNab is a short, pick up and play game where you collect cats under a time limit. In a world where furry creatures roam the realms of plains, forests, and in this section of suburbia... there stands one cat nabbing crusader ready to bring them all home. Step into your shoes, Cat Nabber , and fulfill your destiny .
